qas.question: What does not allow windows to pop up without consent?

plausible_answers.text: the user to open multiple information resources at the same time

qas.question: What do all pop-up blockers allow in a window?
What can be open without the user's consent in a window?

plausible_answers.text: in different tabs of the same window

qas.question: Where do unwanted windows open in a browser?

plausible_answers.text: either in different browser windows or in different tabs of the same window
